PrecisApproval (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with COOPÉRATIVE AGRICOLE DES APICULTEURS DU QUÉBEC which provides for the implementation of a cooperative plan for the marketing of HONEY produced in Quebec during 1991, and (b) for the appointment of ROULEAU, POTVIN, PELLERIN & ASS., chartered accountants, to inspect and audit its books and accounts.
